data.description: Range priced from $334,990 - $345,000. Step into luxury in the heart of Rancho Sahuarita! This meticulously corner lot residence invites you with an open floor plan with split bedrooms. The modern kitchen is a culinary delight with espresso cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and a center island. Plush carpets adorn the bedrooms, while the primary bedroom offers a walk-in closet and a dual-sink and garden tub bathroom. The spacious backyard, complete with a covered patio with room for a pool and much more! Don't let this amazing opportunity for comfort and style pass you by. Plus, enjoy Rancho Sahuarita's abundant amenities - a lake, waterpark, gyms, walking trails, and more! Your dream lifestyle awaits!
